The,Split,API,is,an,application,deployment,platform,that,offers,control,over,software,rollouts,with,a,switchboard,for,feature,flags,targeted,rollout,plans,and,integrations,The,API,is,used,to,build,custom,implementations,or,to,integrate,it,with,a,preexisting,tool,JSON,is,the,preferred,data,format,Split,gives,an,easier,way,to,deliver,specific,features,to,targeted,customers